'''Shadow armor''' was worn by [[Shadowtrooper]]s. The armor was made with [[Cortosis/Legends|cortosis]] to protect the wearer from [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]] damage. It also enhanced [[Stealth field generator/Legends|stealth fields]] that protected the wearer.

